section.section:
"Food" or "food product" includes:
Any meat, meat product, or meat preparation;
Any milk, milk product, or milk preparation;
Any poultry or poultry product; and
Any alcoholic or nonalcoholic beverage.

"Tefillin" includes:
The parchment or other material on which passages from the Bible are to be written;
The writing on that parchment or other material;
The capsules in which the parchment or other material is contained; and
The straps attached to the capsules.
